```

---

🔤 TYPOGRAPHY

• Headings: Playfair Display (600, 700)
• Body: Poppins (400, 500, 600)
• Line height: 1.6 body, 1.2 headings
• Mobile-first with fluid sizing

---

🧱 CORE COMPONENTS

Every layout must support and tag these as semantic HTML:

• NavBar, Hero, CTA, LoginModal, Footer, Sidebar, QuoteBlock
• Card, Accordion, Testimonial, FormField, ButtonPrimary, ButtonAlt
• CRMDashboard, QASearch, ArticlePreview, ResourceList, SupportPrompt
• BlogCard, ProfileCard, ProgressTracker, WellnessWidget

Use semantic HTML5, accessible ARIA tags, alt attributes, and clearly labeled classnames.

---

📐 RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR

All layouts must:
• Be mobile-first
• Include media breakpoints at 768px and 1024px
• Support keyboard navigation
• Follow WCAG 2.1 AA color/contrast compliance
• Auto-adjust containers using Flexbox or CSS Grid

---

🔍 SEO & STRUCTURED DATA

Include:
• OpenGraph meta
• Twitter Card meta
• JSON-LD for blog articles or landing content
• Canonical links
• seo-metadata.json for central configuration

---

🧠 AI BEHAVIOR

Every time this prompt is run:
✅ Scan all existing files and folder names
✅ Apply requested updates with zero overwrite errors
✅ Preserve component state and logic
✅ Create only what's missing or requested
✅ Respond dynamically to user commands

Examples:
• "Add pricing.html page"
• "Convert homepage to Tailwind"
• "Export to Webflow schema"
• "Add newsletter modal"
• "Build light/dark mode toggle"

---

📤 EXPORT FORMATS

Generate on request:
1. .tar.gz archive
2. .prompt file
3. flowchart.svg → full UI path map
4. figma-component-map.json → layers + labels
5. webflow-export.json → Webflow schema
6. manifest.json → PWA support
7. README.md → layout descriptions

---

🧭 FLOWCHART NAVIGATION

User journey:

Landing → Onboarding → Homepage → CRM Dashboard → Content Hub → Q&A → Profile → Login/Auth

---

🧩 COMPONENT COMMENTING

Always include inline HTML comments:

<!-- COMPONENT: CRM Sidebar Navigation | Responsive | ARIA role="navigation" -->

---

🛠 SYSTEM REGENERATION COMMAND

If user says "Regenerate full toolkit":
• Update affected HTML files
• Patch styles.css
• Append flowchart logic
• Adjust SEO metadata
• Repackage exports

---

🧠 REMEMBER

DO NOT guess new pages or features.
DO NOT overwrite existing components unless instructed.
DO NOT add third-party scripts unless requested.
DO build scalable, clean, and accessible frontend code with focus on wellness UX.
